Pierre Blanchar https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pierre_Blanchar 0 Pierre Blanchar (30 June 1892 – 21 November 1963) was a French actor. He appeared in 54 films between 1922 and 1961. Blanchar was married to actress Marthe Vinot, with whom he had a daughter, actress Dominique Blanchar. Pierre_Blanchar ( 30_June_1892 – 21_November_1963 ) was a_French_actor .
